ie-hansen/">Tonie Hansen</option><option value="http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/author/tony-kontzer/">Tony Kontzer</option><option value="http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/author/tony-tamasi/">Tony Tamasi</option><option value="http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/author/ujesh-desai/">Ujesh Desai</option><option value="http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/author/victoria-crimmins/">Victoria Rege</option><option value="http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/author/vishal-lulla/">Vishal Lulla</option><option value="http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/author/warren-ponder/">Warren Ponder</option><option value="http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/author/wayne-young/">Wayne Young</option><option value="http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/author/wenmeihwu/">Wen-mei Hwu</option><option value="http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/author/will-park/">Will Park</option><option value="http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/author/will-ramey/">Will Ramey</option><option value="http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/author/will-wade/">Will Wade</option><option value="http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/author/wolfram-alderson/">Wolfram Alderson</option><option value="http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/author/yanningli/">Yanning Li</option><option value="http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/author/yuriko-nagano/">Yuriko Nagano</option></select><div class="block-bottom"></div></div>		<div id="recent-posts-2" class="widget widget_recent_entries"><div class="block-top"></div>		<h3 class="widget-title">Recent Posts</h3>		<ul>
